context:
KR:
&lt;…? 누구지?&gt;
EN:
&lt;...? Who's there?&gt;

KR:
&lt;선택이랄게 있겠어?&gt;
EN:
&lt;Do we even have a choice?&gt;

KR:
&lt;…휴우. 누군지는 모르겠지만… 고마워.&gt;
EN:
&lt;... Phew. I don't know who you guys are... But thanks.&gt;

KR:
&lt;그런데 이곳엔 왜 정기적으로 들리는 거지?&gt;
EN:
&lt;So why do you guys come here every once in a while, then?&gt;

KR:
&lt;어디로 데려가는 걸까?&gt;
EN:
&lt;Where do you think they're taking us?&gt;

KR:
&lt;우리를 전부 해치려고 하는 거라면…&gt;
EN:
&lt;What if they're leading us into a trap...?&gt;
